MEDIA personality Boity Thulo has revealed her new ride that’s worth no less than R 2 -million. Earlier she posted photos of herself  on her social media platforms at a car delearship standing to a charcoal –coloured Range Rover Lumma CLR RS. A very happy looking Boity,wearing a black pant suit and heels posted , “My incredible baby is finally here! Welcome home, Esther.” According to a Joburg car sales website, a 2019 Lumma CLR RS sells for R2 549 950! Boity  has posted her Mercedes Benz GLA 45 AMG in the past. She surprised many last year when she dropped the Wuz Dat featuring Nasty C  and followed up this year with Ba Kae.  